### Note on Test 7 (Audit Log)
# To verify the audit log captures events, log into HeidiSQL/MySQL client and run:
# SELECT occurred_at, action, target, ip_address FROM audit_log ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 10;

### Task 8 — BONUS: Admin-Only Audit Endpoint
# Expected: 200 OK with logs list if Admin, 403 if Member
GET http://localhost:8000/admin/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json